##  (with respect to the variable order given in <A>rest</A>,
##  if called with two parameters).
##  <P/>
##  Both <A>elim</A> and <A>rest</A> may be a list of variables or a list of
##  variable indices.
##  </Description>
##  </ManSection>
##  <#/GAPDoc>
##
